history.content: Every department handles enrollment differently but the best place to start is to contact the professor. The error message kicks up because undergrads are not allowed to enroll directly into grad level classes without obtaining instructor consent first.

The information you're looking for can be found here: https://www.ischool.berkeley.edu/courses/take-a-class

You can email studentaffairs@ischool.berkeley.edu

I was able to enroll in Info 253B last semester as an undergrad by following these instructions.
